<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٨٨٧٣]</span> عقْبةُ بنُ واصلٍ، ابنُ أخِي مُطرفِ بنِ عَبدِ اللَّهِ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عنْ مُطرّفٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوى عَنهُ الأسودُ بنُ شَيبانَ البصريُّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٨٨٧٤]</span> عقْبةُ بنُ مُكْرَمٍ الضبَّيُّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>عنْ قُدامةَ بنِ حَمَاطةَ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>رَوى عَنهُ مُحمَّدُ بنُ ربيعةَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٨٨٧٥]</span> عقْبةُ بنُ مُكرَمٍ، أبُو عبدِ الملكِ، البَصريُّ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٨٨٧٦]</span> عقْبةُ بنُ مُكرَمٍ الكُوفِيُّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٨٨٧٧]</span> عقْبةُ بنُ مَسروقٍ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>حدَّثَني ميسرةُ بنُ جُهينةَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>سمِعَ منْهُ عبدُ الصَّمدِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>حَديثُهُ في البَصريينَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٨٨٧٨]</span> عُقبةُ الأَسدِيُّ <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عن أَبِي العَلاءِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>رَوى عَنهُ الثَّوريُّ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
